#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:2
msgid "其它"
msgstr "Miscellaneous"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:5
msgid "低精度"
msgstr "Low Precision"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:6
msgid ""
"php中并不是用高精度来存储浮点数，而是用使用 IEEE 754 双精度格式，造成在涉及到浮点数比较的时候可能会出现预期之外的错误。 比如 "
"``php -r \"var_dump(0.2+0.7==0.9);\"`` 这行代码的输出是 ``bool(false)`` 而不是 "
"``bool(true)``。这在一些情况下可能出现问题。"
msgstr ""
"PHP does not store floating-point numbers with high precision; it uses the "
"IEEE 754 double-precision format. This can cause unexpected errors when "
"floating-point values are compared. For example, ``php -r "
"\"var_dump(0.2+0.7==0.9);\"`` outputs ``bool(false)`` instead of "
"``bool(true)``. This may cause problems in some situations."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:10
msgid "弱类型"
msgstr "Weak Typing"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:11
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"如果使用 ``==`` 来判断相等，则会因为类型推断出现一些预料之外的行为，比如magic hash，指当两个md5值都是 "
"``0e[0-9]{30}`` 的时候，就会认为两个hash值相等。 另外在判断字符串和数字的时候，PHP会自动做类型转换，那么 "
"``1==\"1a.php\"`` 的结果会是true"
msgstr ""
"When ``==`` is used for equality checks, type inference may produce "
"unexpected behavior. One example is a magic hash: when two MD5 values both "
"match ``0e[0-9]{30}``, the two hash values are considered equal. In addition, "
"when comparing strings and numbers, PHP automatically performs type "
"conversion, so ``1==\"1a.php\"`` evaluates to true."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:14
msgid "另外在判断一些hash时，如果传入的是数组，返回值会为 ``NULL``, 因此在判断来自网络请求的数据的哈希值时需要先判断数据类型。"
msgstr "Also, when some hash functions receive an array, they return ``NULL``. Therefore, when checking the hash of data from a network request, validate the data type first."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:16
msgid "同样的， ``strcmp()`` ``ereg()`` ``strpos()`` 这些函数在处理数组的时候也会异常，返回NULL。"
msgstr "Similarly, functions such as ``strcmp()``, ``ereg()``, and ``strpos()`` behave abnormally when handling arrays and return NULL."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:19
msgid "命令执行"
msgstr "Command Execution"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:20
msgid "preg_replace 第一个参数是//e的时候，第二个参数会被当作命令执行"
msgstr "When the first argument of preg_replace uses //e, the second argument is executed as code."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:23
msgid "截断"
msgstr "Truncation"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:24
msgid "PHP字符存在截断行为，可以使用 ``ereg`` / ``%00`` / ``iconv`` 等实现php字符截断的操作，从而触发漏洞。"
msgstr "PHP characters can be truncated. Techniques such as ``ereg`` / ``%00`` / ``iconv`` can be used to perform PHP character truncation and trigger vulnerabilities."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:27
msgid "变量覆盖"
msgstr "Variable Overwrite"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:28
msgid ""
"当使用 ``extract`` / ``parse_str`` 等函数时，或者使用php的 ``$$`` "
"特性时，如果没有正确的调用，则可能使得用户可以任意修改变量。"
msgstr ""
"When functions such as ``extract`` / ``parse_str`` are used, or when PHP's "
"``$$`` feature is used, incorrect invocation may allow users to modify "
"variables arbitrarily."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:31
msgid "php特性"
msgstr "PHP Characteristics"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:32
msgid "php自身在解析请求的时候，如果参数名字中包含\" \"、\".\"、\"[\"这几个字符，会将他们转换成下划线"
msgstr "When PHP parses a request, if a parameter name contains \" \", \".\", or \"[\", PHP converts those characters to underscores."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:33
msgid ""
"由于历史原因， ``urlencode`` 和RFC3896存在一定的不同，PHP另外提供了 ``rawurlencode`` "
"对RFC3896完成标准的实现"
msgstr ""
"For historical reasons, ``urlencode`` differs from RFC3896 in some ways. PHP "
"also provides ``rawurlencode`` as a standard-compliant implementation of "
"RFC3896."

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:36
msgid "/tmp临时文件竞争"
msgstr "/tmp Temporary File Race"

#: ../../source/language/php/misc.rst:37
msgid "phpinfo可访问时，可以看到上传的临时文件的路径，从而实现LFI。"
msgstr "When phpinfo is accessible, the path of uploaded temporary files can be observed and used to achieve LFI."
